    </note>Kwa maana kulia kwangu kwa uchungu kwanijia badala ya chakula;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 3:24">kusononeka kwangu kunamwagika kama maji.<verse eid="JOB 3:24"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOB 3:25"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
