    </note>Utalala, wala hakuna atakayekuogofya,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 11:19">naam, wengi watajipendekeza kwako.<verse eid="JOB 11:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 11:20"/>
