    </note>Je, hekima haipatikani katikati ya wazee?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:12">Je, maisha marefu hayaleti ufahamu?<verse eid="JOB 12:12"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 12:13"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
