    </note>“Hekima na nguvu ni vya Mungu;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:13">shauri na ufahamu ni vyake yeye.<verse eid="JOB 12:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 12:14"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
