    </note>Huwaondoa makuhani wakiwa wametekwa nyara,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:19">na kuwaangusha waliojiimarisha muda mrefu.<verse eid="JOB 12:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 12:20"/>
