    </note>Huwamwagia dharau wanaoheshimika,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:21">na kuwavua silaha wenye nguvu.<verse eid="JOB 12:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="JOB 12:22"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 4:5">1Kor 4:5</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 3:5">Ay 3:5</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 139:12">Za 139:12</ref>; <ref loc="DAN 2:22">Dan 2:22</ref></char>
    </note>Hufunua mambo ya ndani ya gizani,</para>
