    </note>Huyafanya mataifa yatukuke na kuyaangamiza;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:23">hufanya mataifa kuwa makubwa, naye huyatawanya.<verse eid="JOB 12:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="JOB 12:24"/>Huwaondolea viongozi wa nchi akili zao;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 12:24">huwapeleka watangetange nyikani pasipo na njia.<verse eid="JOB 12:24"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="JOB 12:25"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">12:25 </char>
