      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 9:24">Ay 9:24</ref>
      </char>
    </note>“Macho yangu yameona hili lote,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 13:1">masikio yangu yamesikia na kulielewa.<verse eid="JOB 13:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="JOB 13:2"/>
