    </note>Je, maneno yenu mengi yasiyo na maana hayana mwisho?</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:3">Mna nini hata mwendelee kushindana kwa maneno?<verse eid="JOB 16:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="JOB 16:4"/>
