      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 29:25">Ay 29:25</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 37:35">Mwa 37:35</ref></char>
    </note>Lakini kinywa changu kingewatia moyo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:5">faraja kutoka midomoni mwangu, ingewaletea nafuu.<verse eid="JOB 16:5"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="JOB 16:6"/>
