      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 6:3">Ay 6:3</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 7:21">7:21</ref></char>
    </note>“Lakini kama nikisema, maumivu yangu bado hayatulizwi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:6">nami kama nikijizuia, wala hayaondoki.<verse eid="JOB 16:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="JOB 16:7"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
