        <ref loc="JDG 8:5">Amu 8:5</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 7:3">Ay 7:3</ref>; <ref loc="JOB 1:19">1:19</ref></char>
    </note>Ee Mungu, hakika umenichakaza;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="JOB 16:7">umewaangamiza kabisa watu wa nyumbani mwangu wote.<verse eid="JOB 16:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
